---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pro jednotlivce – H2OPE" description="Individuální plán podle vašich cílů a potřeb. Vodíková terapie na míru pro každého.">

  <!-- BANNER -->
  <div class="page-banner">
    <div class="container">
      <h1><span class="cs-only">Pro jednotlivce</span><span class="en-only">For Individuals</span></h1>
      <p><span class="cs-only">Individuální plán podle vašich cílů a potřeb.</span><span class="en-only">An individual plan tailored to your goals and needs.</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ZPŮSOB TERAPIE -->
  <section class="therapy-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="therapy-grid">
        <div class="therapy-text">
          <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Jak začít</span><span class="en-only">How to Start</span></p>
          <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Vyberte si způsob terapie</span><span class="en-only">Choose Your Therapy Method</span></h2>
          <p style="font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:2rem">
            <span class="cs-only">Nabízíme individuální konzultaci a pronájem vodíkového stroje k vám domů. Vše nastavíme na míru a váš pokrok sledujeme v aplikaci FlowGen.</span>
            <span class="en-only">We offer individual consultation and rental of a hydrogen machine to your home. We set everything up to measure and track your progress in the FlowGen app.</span>
          </p>
          <button type="button" class="btn btn-orange" data-open-modal="contact"><span class="cs-only">Chci nezávaznou konzultaci →</span><span class="en-only">I want a free consultation →</span></button>
        </div>
        <div class="therapy-visual">
          <img src="/images/h2ope-product-side-CxX-ZJVh.png" alt="H2OPE přístroj" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JAK TO FUNGUJE - 4 KROKY -->
  <section class="steps4-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Proces</span><span class="en-only">Process</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Jak to funguje</span><span class="en-only">How It Works</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Jednoduchý proces od konzultace po pravidelnou terapii doma.</span><span class="en-only">Simple process from consultation to regular therapy at home.</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="steps4-grid">
        <div class="step4-card">
          <div class="step4-num">01</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Individuální konzultace</span><span class="en-only">Individual Consultation</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Společně si ujasníme cíle a doporučíme vhodný postup. Konzultace je nezávazná a trvá přibližně 30 minut.</span><span class="en-only">Together we clarify your goals and recommend the right approach. The consultation is free and takes approximately 30 minutes.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step4-card">
          <div class="step4-num">02</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Nastavení FlowGen</span><span class="en-only">FlowGen Setup</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Propojíme vás s aplikací FlowGen pro sledování individuálního pokroku. Vše nastavíme a vysvětlíme.</span><span class="en-only">We'll connect you with the FlowGen app for tracking individual progress. We'll set everything up and explain it.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step4-card">
          <div class="step4-num">03</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Pronájem stroje domů</span><span class="en-only">Home Machine Rental</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Zapůjčíme vám vodíkový stroj domů, abyste mohli inhalovat pravidelně a pohodlně ve svém prostředí.</span><span class="en-only">We loan you a hydrogen machine at home so you can inhale regularly and comfortably in your own environment.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step4-card">
          <div class="step4-num">04</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Vyhodnocení a optimalizace</span><span class="en-only">Evaluation & Optimization</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Analyzujeme data z aplikace a průběžně upravujeme program tak, aby dával smysl vašemu tělu i režimu.</span><span class="en-only">We analyze data from the app and continuously adjust the program so it makes sense for your body and lifestyle.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VÝHODY -->
  <section class="benefits-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label"><span class="cs-only">Benefity</span><span class="en-only">Benefits</span></p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Výhody vodíkové terapie</span><span class="en-only">Benefits of Hydrogen Therapy</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Co lidé na vodíkové terapii nejčastěji oceňují. Jednoduše a srozumitelně.</span><span class="en-only">What people most often appreciate about hydrogen therapy. Simply and clearly explained.</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="benefits8-grid">
        <div class="benefit8">
          <div class="b8-icon">💧</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Hydratace organismu</span><span class="en-only">Body Hydration</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Podporuje optimální fungování buněk a regulaci tělesné teploty.</span><span class="en-only">Supports optimal cell function and body temperature regulation.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit8">
          <div class="b8-icon">⚡</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Rychlejší regenerace</span><span class="en-only">Faster Recovery</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Pomáhá eliminovat kyselinu mléčnou po fyzické aktivitě.</span><span class="en-only">Helps eliminate lactic acid after physical activity.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit8">
          <div class="b8-icon">✨</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Podpora zdraví pleti</span><span class="en-only">Skin Health Support</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Redukuje oxidační stres a podporuje přirozenou obnovu pokožky.</span><span class="en-only">Reduces oxidative stress and supports natural skin renewal.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit8">
          <div class="b8-icon">🧠</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Mentální výkon</span><span class="en-only">Mental Performance</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Pozitivně ovlivňuje kognitivní funkce, paměť a soustředění.</span><span class="en-only">Positively influences cognitive functions, memory, and concentration.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit8">
          <div class="b8-icon">❤️</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Kardiovaskulární podpora</span><span class="en-only">Cardiovascular Support</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Přispívá ke snížení oxidace LDL cholesterolu.</span><span class="en-only">Contributes to reduced LDL cholesterol oxidation.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit8">
          <div class="b8-icon">🔋</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Více energie</span><span class="en-only">More Energy</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Podporuje energetický metabolismus na buněčné úrovni.</span><span class="en-only">Supports energy metabolism at the cellular level.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit8">
          <div class="b8-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Imunitní systém</span><span class="en-only">Immune System</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Moduluje imunitní odpověď a podporuje obranyschopnost.</span><span class="en-only">Modulates immune response and supports immunity.</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="benefit8">
          <div class="b8-icon">🌿</div>
          <h3><span class="cs-only">Celková vitalita</span><span class="en-only">Overall Vitality</span></h3>
          <p><span class="cs-only">Zlepšuje fyzický výkon a pocit životní energie.</span><span class="en-only">Improves physical performance and sense of life energy.</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TÉMATA -->
  <section class="topics-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="topics-grid">
        <div class="topics-text">
          <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="cs-only">Kde se o vodíku nejčastěji mluví</span>
            <span class="en-only">Where Hydrogen Is Most Discussed</span>
          </h2>
          <p style="color:var(--gray);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.5rem">
            <span class="cs-only">Oblast, ve kterých se molekulární vodík často mluví a zkoumá. Vodíková terapie není léčba, ale podporuje wellness program zaměřený na vitalitu a regeneraci.</span>
            <span class="en-only">The areas where molecular hydrogen is often discussed and studied. Hydrogen therapy is not treatment, but supports a wellness program focused on vitality and recovery.</span>
          </p>
          <p class="topics-disclaimer">
            <span class="cs-only">Vodíková terapie není léčba, ale podporuje wellness program. V případě zdravotních potíží se poraďte s lékařem.</span>
            <span class="en-only">Hydrogen therapy is not treatment, but supports a wellness program. For health concerns, consult a doctor.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="topics-tags">
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Sportovní výkon a regenerace</span><span class="en-only">Sports Performance & Recovery</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Celková vitalita a energie</span><span class="en-only">Overall Vitality & Energy</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Mentální pohoda a soustředění</span><span class="en-only">Mental Wellbeing & Focus</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Podpora imunitního systému</span><span class="en-only">Immune System Support</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Metabolické zdraví</span><span class="en-only">Metabolic Health</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Kardiovaskulární podpora</span><span class="en-only">Cardiovascular Support</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Kvalita spánku</span><span class="en-only">Sleep Quality</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Stres a únava</span><span class="en-only">Stress & Fatigue</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Zdraví kůže a pokožky</span><span class="en-only">Skin & Skin Health</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Zánětlivé stavy</span><span class="en-only">Inflammatory Conditions</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Detoxikace organismu</span><span class="en-only">Body Detoxification</span></span>
          <span class="topic-tag"><span class="cs-only">Podpora regenerace tkání</span><span class="en-only">Tissue Regeneration</span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="faq-section section-gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="text-center">
        <p class="section-label">FAQ</p>
        <h2 class="section-title"><span class="cs-only">Často kladené dotazy</span><span class="en-only">Frequently Asked Questions</span></h2>
        <p class="section-sub"><span class="cs-only">Odpovědi na nejčastější otázky o pronájmu stroje domů.</span><span class="en-only">Answers to the most common questions about home machine rental.</span></p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><span class="cs-only">Jak funguje pronájem stroje domů?</span><span class="en-only">How does home machine rental work?</span></summary>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p><span class="cs-only">Po konzultaci a nastavení vašeho individuálního plánu vám zapůjčíme přístroj přímo domů. Přístroj nainstalujeme a vše vysvětlíme. Stroj vrátíte po dohodnuté době nebo po splnění programu.</span><span class="en-only">After the consultation and setting up your individual plan, we loan you the device directly at home. We install the device and explain everything. You return the machine after the agreed period or after completing the program.</span></p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><span class="cs-only">Jak často se obvykle inhaluje?</span><span class="en-only">How often do you typically inhale?</span></summary>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p><span class="cs-only">Frekvence inhalací závisí na vašem individuálním plánu. Většina klientů inhaluje 1–2x denně po dobu 20–60 minut. Konkrétní doporučení dostanete po konzultaci.</span><span class="en-only">Inhalation frequency depends on your individual plan. Most clients inhale 1–2 times a day for 20–60 minutes. You'll receive specific recommendations after the consultation.</span></p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><span class="cs-only">Jak mi pomůže aplikace FlowGen?</span><span class="en-only">How will the FlowGen app help me?</span></summary>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p><span class="cs-only">FlowGen sleduje váš pokrok, připomíná vám sezení a pomáhá nám optimalizovat váš plán na základě reálných dat. Máte vše přehledně na jednom místě.</span><span class="en-only">FlowGen tracks your progress, reminds you of sessions, and helps us optimize your plan based on real data. You have everything neatly in one place.</span></p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><span class="cs-only">Pro koho je program vhodný?</span><span class="en-only">Who is the program suitable for?</span></summary>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p><span class="cs-only">Program je vhodný pro dospělé, kteří chtějí aktivně pečovat o své zdraví a wellbeing. Před zahájením provedeme konzultaci, abychom ověřili vhodnost pro váš konkrétní případ.</span><span class="en-only">The program is suitable for adults who want to actively care for their health and wellbeing. Before starting, we conduct a consultation to verify suitability for your specific case.</span></p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><span class="cs-only">Co potřebuji doma?</span><span class="en-only">What do I need at home?</span></summary>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p><span class="cs-only">Stačí elektrická zásuvka a klidné místo na sezení. Přístroj je kompaktní a tichý – nezasáhne do vašeho každodenního života.</span><span class="en-only">All you need is an electrical outlet and a quiet place to sit. The device is compact and quiet – it won't interfere with your daily life.</span></p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary><span class="cs-only">Jak rychle můžeme začít?</span><span class="en-only">How quickly can we start?</span></summary>
          <div class="faq-body">
            <p><span class="cs-only">Po první konzultaci a nastavení plánu obvykle začínáme do 1–2 týdnů. Kontaktujte nás a domluvíme se na konkrétním termínu.</span><span class="en-only">After the first consultation and plan setup, we usually start within 1–2 weeks. Contact us and we'll agree on a specific date.</span></p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2><span class="cs-only">Nejste si jistí jak vám vodík pomůže?</span><span class="en-only">Not sure how hydrogen can help you?</span></h2>
      <p><span class="cs-only">Pojďme se spojit na 15 min, kde Vám vše ukážeme a vysvětlíme</span><span class="en-only">Let's connect for 15 min and we'll show and explain everything</span></p>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-orange" data-open-modal="contact"><span class="cs-only">Chci nezávaznou konzultaci</span><span class="en-only">I want a free consultation</span></button>
      <p class="cta-note"><span class="cs-only">Konzultace je nezávazná. Lidský přístup.</span><span class="en-only">Consultation is free. Human approach.</span></p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  /* THERAPY */
  .therapy-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .therapy-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .therapy-visual { border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(26,58,92,0.15); }
  .therapy-visual img { width: 100%; display: block; }

  /* STEPS 4 */
  .steps4-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .steps4-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .step4-card {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 2rem;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(26,58,92,0.07);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--cyan);
  }
  .step4-num { font-size: 2.2rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--cyan); opacity: 0.25; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .step4-card h3 { font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .step4-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.65; }

  /* BENEFITS 8 */
  .benefits-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .benefits8-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1.25rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .benefit8 {
    background: var(--gray-light);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.25s, background 0.25s;
  }
  .benefit8:hover { background: var(--white); transform: translateY(-4px); box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(26,58,92,0.1); }
  .b8-icon { font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .benefit8 h3 { font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue); margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .benefit8 p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.6; }

  /* TOPICS */
  .topics-section { padding: 5rem 0; background: var(--gray-light); }
  .topics-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: start; }
  .topics-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.65rem; }
  .topic-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--blue);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 100px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(26,58,92,0.1);
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
  }
  .topic-tag:hover { background: var(--cyan); color: var(--white); border-color: var(--cyan); }
  .topics-disclaimer { font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--gray); opacity: 0.8; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* FLOWGEN */
  .flowgen-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .flowgen-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 4rem; align-items: center; }
  .fg-tagline { font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--cyan); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .fg-features { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.85rem; margin-top: 1rem; }
  .fg-feature { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 500; }
  .fgf-icon {
    width: 42px; height: 42px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .fg-visual { border-radius: 20px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }
  .fg-visual img { width: 100%; display: block; }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-section { padding: 5rem 0; }
  .faq-list { max-width: 760px; margin: 2rem auto 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.75rem; }
  .faq-item {
    background: var(--white);
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(26,58,92,0.06);
  }
  .faq-item summary {
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--blue);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    transition: background 0.2s;
  }
  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-item summary::after { content: '+'; font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 300; color: var(--cyan); flex-shrink: 0; }
  .faq-item[open] summary::after { content: '−'; }
  .faq-item summary:hover { background: var(--gray-light); }
  .faq-item[open] summary { background: var(--gray-light); }
  .faq-body { padding: 0 1.5rem 1.25rem; }
  .faq-body p { font-size: 0.93rem; color: var(--gray); line-height: 1.7; }

  @media (max-width: 1000px) {
    .benefits8-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .therapy-grid, .flowgen-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .steps4-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .fg-visual { order: -1; }
    .therapy-visual img, .fg-visual img { max-height: 280px; object-fit: cover; }
    .topics-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2rem; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .benefits8-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
